data.description: Looking for a spacious home close to town, hospital, restaurants and the interstate, your search is over. 311 Tara Estates offers a generous layout with 6 bedrooms, and three full bathrooms, two have walk-in showers providing ample space for a growing family or accommodating guests! It features two kitchens upstairs and down. The living room has a fireplace and large windows for natural lighting. And there is plenty of storage space with several closets in convenient locations. Downstairs has several windows that allow natural lighting, and a smaller bedroom that would make a nice office space. It also has a propane fireplace in the kitchen/dining area. There is an oversized 2-car garage and a large deck on the back of the house. This property provides an excellent opportunity for the buyers to personalize the home with your style of decor and colors and has been priced accordingly. So don't miss out on this unique chance to transform this house into a place you can call home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and let your imagination run wild and envision the possibilities that await you at 311 Tara Estates.
